Is your storeroom filled with scrap and old things? You are at the right place. It's time to clean your house and sell your scrap to us. Sell your Kabad to us.

About Scrap Spot

Scrap Spot is a revolutionary start-up based in Pune, dedicated to transforming waste management. Our mission is to create a cleaner, greener future by providing efficient and eco-friendly scrap collection services right at your doorstep.

Eco-Friendly

Convenient

Best Rates

From aluminum cans to old appliances, we recycle it all.
